From 303b37ffda178dbc7dd9f8097ddfcff3ec079d28 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Stick Pro Agent <agent@stickpro.local>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:10:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] security(P0): remove hardcoded JWT_SECRET fallback

- Fail fast at startup if JWT_SECRET is missing when ENVIRONMENT=production
- Keep clearly-marked insecure fallback only in development/testing
- Apply the same guard in backend/server.py, backend/core/security.py and
  backend/routes/auth.py (the three places that previously hardcoded
  'roller-hockey-hub-secret-key-2024')
- Add backend/.env.example documenting required variables
- Add backend/tests/test_jwt_secret_validation.py covering prod-abort,
  dev-fallback, explicit-secret and a regression guard for the legacy string
- .gitignore: allow committing *.env.example templates

No authentication logic changes.
